    8 888888888o.   8 8888         8 888888888o.
    8 8888    `88.  8 8888         8 8888    `^888.
    8 8888     `88  8 8888         8 8888        `88.
    8 8888     ,88  8 8888         8 8888         `88
    8 8888.   ,88'  8 8888         8 8888          88
    8 888888888P'   8 8888         8 8888          88
    8 8888`8b       8 8888         8 8888         ,88
    8 8888 `8b.     8 8888         8 8888        ,88'
    8 8888   `8b.   8 8888         8 8888    ,o88P'
    8 8888     `88. 8 888888888888 8 888888888P'


    (OS X only, Chrome only, patches welcome)

    Reloads the frontmost browser tab. E.g.

        rld chrome

    Can also reload just the linked CSS

        rld chrome-css
    
    To install with NPM (Node Packaged Modules)
    
        npm install -g rld
    
    Or from source
        
        git clone https://github.com/quackingduck/rld.git
        cd rld
        make install
